Password
========

### Dependencies

- PHP 5.3+

### Usage

```php
<?php
  
  // hash a given passphrase
  $hash = lib\password::hash( 'passphrase' );
  
  // check a given passphrase against
  // the stored hash
  if( lib\password::check( 'passphrase', $storedHash ) ) {
    // they match, we're good to go...
